INSTALLATION (to be done)
    GRETA can be easily compiled and installed. The Animated Execution Plugin
    (hub.top.GRETA.run) requires the packages specified in the file
    META-INF/MANIFEST.MF in the 'Require-Bundle' section. Most packages are
    provides by Eclipse and standard plugins (see www.eclipse.org). The following
    non-standard packages are required:
    
    * hub.top.GRETA.diagram (and its dependencies) available from
      svn://svn.gna.org/svn/service-tech/trunk/greta/
      
    * hub.top.editor.resource and hub.top.editor.ptnetLoLA available from
      svn://svn.gna.org/svn/service-tech/trunk/seda/
      
    * hub.top.uma available from
      svn://svn.gna.org/svn/service-tech/trunk/Service-Tech-Java/uma

DOCUMENTATION
    The directory "doc" contains a documentation of GRETA.
